<div>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.1 (STRIPS 2, 1) MACHENGYUAN 5: 268 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.1">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.2">延陵季子,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.3">其天民也乎!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.4">生</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.5">而不因其俗.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.6">吳人生七年</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.7">【2】而動散,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.8">文乎其膺 (胸),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.9">延陵季子僑(矯)</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.10">而弗受.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.11">延陵季子,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-1a.12">其天民也乎!</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.2 (STRIPS 1, 23,7) MACHENGYUAN 5: 268, 281, 272 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a.1">子貢 [曰:]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a.2">【1】[...] 何? [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a.3">仁之有.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a.4">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a.5">“列乎其下,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a.6">不折其枝,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a.7">飤其實【23】 [者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-2a.8">不毀其器] [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.3 (STRIPS 7, 8) MACHENGYUAN 5: 272 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.1">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.2">“吾聞父母之喪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.3">【7】食肉如飯土,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.4">飲酒如淆,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.5">信乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.6">子貢曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.7">“莫親乎父母,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.8">死不顧,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.9">生可言乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.10">其信也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-3a.11">子【8】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.4 (STRIP 10) MACHENGYUAN 5: 273 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a.1">[...] 汝弗知也呼?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a.2">由!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a.3">夫以衆犯難,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a.4">以親受祿,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a.5">勞以成事,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a.6">印以擅 [樹]官,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a.7">士治 [鉤]以力</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-4a.8">則俎以【10】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.5 (STRIPS 17, 20) MACHENGYUAN 5: 277, 279 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.1">[...] 弗王,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.2">善矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.3">夫焉能王人?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.4">由!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.5">子過曹,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.6">[顏]【17】淵馭.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.7">至老丘,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.8">有戎(農)植其槈</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-5a.9">而歌焉.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.6 (STRIPS 20, 4) MACHENGYUAN 5: 279, 269 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.1">子據乎軾而[...]【20】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.2">[...] 風也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.3">亂節</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.4">而哀聲.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.5">曹之喪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.6">其必此乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.7">“回!”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.8">子嘆曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-6a.9">“烏!莫我知也夫!”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.7 (STRIPS 4, 21, 22) MACHENGYUAN 5: 269 , 280 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a.1">子遊曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a.2">“有地[施]之謂也乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a.3">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a.4">偃【4】吾未見華[邦]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a.5">而信者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a.6">未見善事人</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a.7">而憂者.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-7a.8">今之世[...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.8 (STRIPS 22, 13) MACHENGYUAN 5: 280, 275 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-8a.1">[...] 子聞之曰: [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-8a.2">“賜,不吾智知也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-8a.3">夙興夜寐,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-8a.4">以求聞 [...]【22】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-8a.5">[不...以 ] 就人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-8a.6">不曲防以去人.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.9 (STRIPS 13, 12) MACHENGYUAN 5: 275 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.1">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.2">“君子亡所不足,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.3">無所有餘,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.4">蓋 【13】[..] 也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.5">求為之言.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.6">有夫言也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.7">求為之行.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.8">言行相近,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-9a.9">然後君子.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.10 (STRIPS 12, 15, 16) MACHENGYUAN 5: 275, 276, 277 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-10a.1">子【12】曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-10a.2">“回! 來,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-10a.3">吾告汝.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-10a.4">其阻絕乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-10a.5">雖多聞</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-10a.6">而不友賢,其【15】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-10a.7">[...] 焉終.” [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.11 (STRIP 16) MACHENGYUAN 5: 277 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a.1">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a.2">“寡聞“</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a.3">則孤,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a.4">寡見</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a.5">則肆.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a.6">多聞</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a.7">則惑,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-11a.8">多見則[...] 【16】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.12 (STRIPS 5, 6) MACHENGYUAN 5: 270, 271 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a" ed="tls" n="001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a.1">[...] 者,可逆而造也.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a.2">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a.3">“小子來,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a.4">取余言:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a.5">登年不恆至,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a.6">耈老不復壯,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a.7">賢者忣【5】[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-12a.8">[...] 焉.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.13 (STRIPS 6, 9) MACHENGYUAN 5: 271, 273 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a" ed="tls" n="001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.1">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.2">“貧賤</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.3">而不約者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.4">吾見之矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.5">富貴</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.6">而不驕者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.7">吾聞</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.8">而[未之見也.”]【6】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.9">[...] 士,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.10">吾見之矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.11">事</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.12">而弗受者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.13">吾聞</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-13a.14">而未之見也.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.14 (STRIP 9) MACHENGYUAN 5: 273 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-14a" ed="tls" n="001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-14a.1">子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-14a.2">“人而下臨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-14a.3">猶上臨也.【9】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.15 (STRIP 11) MACHENGYUAN 5: 274 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-15a" ed="tls" n="001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-15a.1">曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-15a.2">“巧言令色,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-15a.3">未可謂仁也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-15a.4">[.] 者其言,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-15a.5">[.]而不可.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-15a.6">[...] 此之謂仁.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.16 (STRIPS 11, 24) MACHENGYUAN 5: 274, 281 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-16a" ed="tls" n="001-16a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-16a.1">宰我問君子.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-16a.2">曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-16a.3">“予! 汝能慎始與終,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-16a.4">斯善矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-16a.5">為君子乎?【11】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-16a.6">汝焉能也.”【24】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.17 (STRIP 19) MACHENGYUAN 5:278 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-17a" ed="tls" n="001-17a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-17a.1">長,蓬伯玉止乎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-17a.2">子惇惇如也;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-17a.3">聽子路往乎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-17a.4">子愕愕如也;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-17a.5">如誅【19】[...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.DIZIWEN 5.26.18 (STRIP 14) MACHENGYUAN 5: 276 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-18a" ed="tls" n="001-18a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-18a.1">從吾子</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-18a.2">皆能有侍乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-18a.3">君子道昭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0055_tls_001-18a.4">然則夫二三子者 【14】</seg></p>

